data.description: Stunning 5 Bedroom/5 Bathroom 2 Story House with a beautiful pool in a beautiful and quiet residential area of Richmond West. Garage has been converted into a room with a full bathroom. The entire interior was completely redone in 2022 with Hurricane impact windows and doors throughout. All appliances are brand new with warranty. Every bedroom comes with a remote controlled ceiling fan. The entire house has slim recessed LED lighting. This home has two AC units (top/bottom) and has SMART thermostats. Has a beautiful pool to enjoy all year long and comes with a small backyard shelter for extra storage. A+ Schools nearby and conveniently close to Turnpike and Krome.
